 I can't demonstrate it well because the car has to be in motion, but

3
00:00:05,660 --> 00:00:08,800
 on my Leaf there's an option screen, and it lets you change the time and

4
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:11,430
 the date, and some other options on the car.

5
