 But at that point, the menu blocks you from using it,

7
00:00:16,730 --> 00:00:19,250
 saying you can only use it when the car is at rest.

8
00:00:19,250 --> 00:00:20,270
 That's for safety reasons.

9
00:00:20,270 --> 00:00:23,380
 They don't want people fiddling with the option screen while driving.

10
00:00:23,380 --> 00:00:24,230
 What makes it interesting,

11
00:00:24,230 --> 00:00:27,130
 though, is it's a constraint that isn't in the service of usability,

12
00:00:27,130 --> 00:00:29,030
 it's in the service of safety.

13
00:00:29,030 --> 00:00:29,030
 The car is made less usable to make it more safe.

